OL,4,Cchildren sentenced to 20 years
OL,6,FA victim of a pedophile surgeon has
OL,7,Ftold ITV News he is a "monster" -
OL,8,Fafter one of France's biggest ever
OL,9,Fchild sex abuse cases. ITV News
OL,10,FReporter Sam Holder has the latest
OL,12,FA 74-year-old former surgeon, who
OL,13,Fraped hundreds of victims over a
OL,14,Fperiod spanning more than two decades,
OL,15,Fhas been sentenced to a maximum of 20
OL,16,Fyears in prison by a French court.
OL,18,FJoel Le Scouarnec was found guilty of
OL,19,Fraping and sexually assaulting 299
OL,20,Fchildren.
