OL,6,FLe Scouarnec is already serving a 15-
OL,7,Fyear prison sentence, for a conviction
OL,8,Fin 2020 for the rape and sexual
OL,9,Fassault of four children, including
OL,10,Ftwo nieces.
OL,12,FHe had told the court that he had
OL,13,Fcommitted "despicable acts" over 25
OL,14,Fyears while working as a doctor in
OL,15,Fwestern France.
OL,17,FThe new trial in Brittany began in
OL,18,FFebruary and laid bare a pattern of
OL,19,Fabuse between 1989 and 2014.
