OL,6,FMost of the victims were unconscious
OL,7,For sedated hospital patients at the
OL,8,Ftime of the assaults. The average age
OL,9,Fwas 11.
OL,11,FVictims and their families have
OL,12,Fpublicly asked why local and national
OL,13,Fhealth authorities failed to stop Le
OL,14,FScouarnec.
OL,16,FIn 2005, he was convicted of
OL,17,Fdownloading images of child sexual
OL,18,Fabuse and received a suspended jail
OL,19,Fsentence, but managed to continue
OL,20,Fworking in public hospitals.
