OL,6,FDecades of abuse
OL,8,FDozens of victims and rights
OL,9,Fcampaigners gathered outside the
OL,10,Fcourthouse ahead of the verdict.
OL,12,FMany of those in attendance held a
OL,13,Fbanner made of hundreds of white paper
OL,14,Fwith black silhouettes - one for each
OL,15,Fvictim.
OL,17,FThe trial comes as activists are
OL,18,Fpushing to lift taboos that have long
OL,19,Fsurrounded sexual abuse in France.
