OL,6,FThe full extent of Le Scouarnec's
OL,7,Fabuse was revealed when he was re-
OL,8,Farrested in 2017 on suspicion of
OL,9,Fraping his six-year-old neighbour.
OL,11,FLe Scouarnec kept detailed notes of
OL,12,Fall the assaults he carried out, which
OL,13,Fis how police identified many of the
OL,14,Fvictims.
OL,16,FThe notes, which form the backbone of
OL,17,Fthe trial, were recovered during the
OL,18,Finvestigation into a separate child
OL,19,Fsexual abuse case, for which he was
OL,20,Fconvicted of assaulting four children.
